  <div xmlns:v="http://rdf.data-vocabulary.org/#" typeof="v:Review">
    <div class="main review-item" id="2959835">
        

  <header class="main-hd">
    <h3 class="title">
      <a href="https://book.douban.com/review/2959835/" class="title-link">一封墙外青年的家书----读《李陵答苏武书》</a>
      <div class="toggle_review right">        <a href="javascript:;" id="toggle-2959835"class="indicator unfold j" title="展开全文">        </a>
      </div>
    </h3>
    

<div class="header-more">
    <a class="author-avatar" href="https://www.douban.com/people/voga/"><img width="48" height="48" src="https://img3.doubanio.com/icon/u4271422-30.jpg"></a>
    <a href="https://www.douban.com/people/voga/" class="author">
      <span property="v:reviewer">小和尚</span>
    </a>    <span property="v:rating" class="allstar50 main-title-rating" title="力荐"></span>
  <span property="v:dtreviewed" content="2010-01-27"
      class="main-meta">2010-01-27 22:36:19</span>
</div>

  </header>

        <div class="main-bd">
          <div id="review_2959835_short" class="review-short">
            <div class="short-content">
                          《古文观止》里的这一篇，较少有人提及。对于李陵其人，也是鲜有人知。但是与他相关的著名历史公案，却因为司马迁的史笔传扬千古。司马迁正是为李陵仗义上书而受腐刑的。他把因此而来的满腔忿恨化成曲笔，婉转地刺向了当时的统治者。         另一位男主角的名声可就大...

                    <a class="pl" href="https://book.douban.com/review/2959835/#comments">(20回应)</a>
                  <div class="more-info pl clearfix">
                    <span class="left">45有用 / 0没用</span>
                        <span class="publisher left">
                            中华书局1959版</span>
                  </div>
            </div>
          </div>
          <div id="review_2959835_full" class="hidden">
            <div id="review_2959835_full_content" class="full-content"></div>
